  "description": "<p>Position: <strong>Interior Designer (Sales & Project Management)</strong></p><p><em>Work Schedule: </em><em><strong>Flexible schedule with full commitment</strong></em></p><p><em>Requirements: </em><em><strong>Attitude and willingness to learn matter most.</strong></em><br /></p><p>Love creating beautiful spaces and want to grow in a supportive team?<br /></p><p>We’re building a team of designers who take pride in quality, responsibility, and delivering a calm, confident renovation experience.<br /></p><p>This role involves both design work and sales responsibility. If you enjoy client interaction and closing projects, you’ll enjoy this role.<br /></p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</em></p>",
