    "description": "<p>Join our passionate team as a Sales Interior Designer, where creativity meets strategy. In this dynamic role, you'll not only craft stunning interior concepts tailored to each client's lifestyle, but also play a key part in driving sales and growing our brand presence. From the first consultation to project completion, you’ll guide homeowners through a seamless renovation journey — offering expert design advice, building strong client relationships, and closing deals with confidence.</p>\n<p><br>\nIf you have an eye for design, a flair for communication, and a hunger to succeed in a fast-paced, rewarding environment — we’d love to meet you.</p>",
